{"title":"Macworld Podcast: Your hot takes on RCS coming to iPhone, Mac RAM, and more","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2158138/macworld-podcast-your-hot-takes-on-rcs-coming-to-iphone-mac-ram-and-more.html","date":1701936000000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>This episode is all about Macworld reader and listener hot takes. You have thoughts and we’re going to share and respond to what you wrote—and on this show, it’s on two recent topics specifically.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is episode 866 with <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Jason-Cross/\" target=\"_blank\">Jason Cross</a>, <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Michael-Simon/\" target=\"_blank\">Michael Simon</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Roman-Loyola/\" target=\"_blank\">Roman Loyola</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Listen to episode 866 on Apple Podcasts</h2>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2>Listen to episode 866 on Spotify</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>RCS on the iPhone </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>On November 17, 2023, hell froze over. That was the day that Apple announced that <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2141884/iphone-imessage-rcs-support-later-in-2024.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rich Communication Services (RCS) will be coming to the iPhone later next year</a>. For those who don’t know what RCS is, essentially what it will do is make the experience of sending messages between the iPhone and Android much better. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The news spurred a lot of people to post <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.facebook.com/Macworld/posts/pfbid02xeXddaUj3dXjzSSjsCz5W6deFVvdcPELrNaDwKsENrwa6GXiNbgfUVGyxM61NE52l&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">their opinions on the Macworld Facebook page</a>.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jim-coffey-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"jim coffey facebook\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jim-coffey-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jim-coffey-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C108&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jim-coffey-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C276&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jim-coffey-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1200%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jim-coffey-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1536%2C553&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jim-coffey-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=2048%2C737&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"432\" /></figure><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.facebook.com/Macworld/posts/pfbid02xeXddaUj3dXjzSSjsCz5W6deFVvdcPELrNaDwKsENrwa6GXiNbgfUVGyxM61NE52l&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></div>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/greg-crary-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"greg crary facebook\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/greg-crary-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/greg-crary-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C53&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/greg-crary-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C135&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/greg-crary-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1200%2C211&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/greg-crary-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1536%2C269&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/greg-crary-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=2048%2C359&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"211\" /></figure><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.facebook.com/Macworld/posts/pfbid02xeXddaUj3dXjzSSjsCz5W6deFVvdcPELrNaDwKsENrwa6GXiNbgfUVGyxM61NE52l&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></div>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chet-morgan-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"chet morgan facebook\" width=\"1200\" height=\"210\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chet-morgan-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chet-morgan-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C53&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chet-morgan-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C135&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chet-morgan-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1200%2C211&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chet-morgan-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1536%2C269&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/chet-morgan-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=2048%2C359&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" /></figure><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.facebook.com/Macworld/posts/pfbid02xeXddaUj3dXjzSSjsCz5W6deFVvdcPELrNaDwKsENrwa6GXiNbgfUVGyxM61NE52l&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></div>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-brand-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"john brand facebook\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-brand-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-brand-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C35&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-brand-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C88&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-brand-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1200%2C138&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-brand-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1536%2C177&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-brand-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=2048%2C236&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"138\" /></figure><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.facebook.com/Macworld/posts/pfbid02xeXddaUj3dXjzSSjsCz5W6deFVvdcPELrNaDwKsENrwa6GXiNbgfUVGyxM61NE52l&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></div>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/noah-norton-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"noah norton facebook\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/noah-norton-rcs-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/noah-norton-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C34&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/noah-norton-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C88&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/noah-norton-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1200%2C138&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/noah-norton-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=1536%2C176&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/noah-norton-rcs-facebook.jpg?resize=2048%2C235&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"138\" /></figure><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.facebook.com/Macworld/posts/pfbid02xeXddaUj3dXjzSSjsCz5W6deFVvdcPELrNaDwKsENrwa6GXiNbgfUVGyxM61NE52l&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>8GB or unified memory in a pro Mac </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>About a month ago Jason wrote an article about the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2130071/entry-level-m3-macbook-pro-8gb-memory-ram-performance.html\" target=\"_blank\">8GB of memory in the base model of the MacBook Pro and how it’s not enough</a>. Even though <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2130974/bob-borchers-defends-8gb-ram-macbook-pro-analogous-to-16gb-pc.html\" target=\"_blank\">Apple thinks 8GB on the Mac is equal to 16GB on a Windows PC</a>, we’ve easily been in situations where the consumer apps being used need more than 8GB.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n<blockquote><p>As befits the most negative Mac oriented outfit, Macworld’s writer once again projects their usage case to negativity slam Apple. Most people do not use any Electron apps. Since I use Safari I will regularly have 100-200 tabs, no issues. Maybe 15%-20% genuinely need more than 8GB</p>— Gene Thomas (@16YearsAtTheFS) <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://twitter.com/16YearsAtTheFS/status/1725546503781883979?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">November 17, 2023</a></blockquote> \n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n<blockquote><p>Electron &amp; Javascript to blame for its memory hunger nature…<br />Non-user replaceable/upgradable Flash-SSD and RAM it's a suicide for all 8Gb RAM models…<br />Consumer right to upgrade and repair needs to happen.</p>— JSMN (@jsmnX) <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://twitter.com/jsmnX/status/1722749181196935421?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\">November 9, 2023</a></blockquote> \n</div></figure>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/geometricreflex-threads.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"geometricreflext threads\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/geometricreflex-threads.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/geometricreflex-threads.jpg?resize=300%2C96&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/geometricreflex-threads.jpg?resize=768%2C245&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/geometricreflex-threads.jpg?resize=1200%2C383&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/geometricreflex-threads.jpg?resize=1536%2C490&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/geometricreflex-threads.jpg?resize=2048%2C654&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"383\" /></figure><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.threads.net/@macworld_hq/post/CzZSi0SvpAz&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Threads</a></div>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/charles-lindauer-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"charles lindauer facebook\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/charles-lindauer-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/charles-lindauer-facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C62&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/charles-lindauer-facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C159&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/charles-lindauer-facebook.jpg?resize=1200%2C249&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/charles-lindauer-facebook.jpg?resize=1536%2C319&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/charles-lindauer-facebook.jpg?resize=2048%2C425&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"249\" /></figure><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.facebook.com/Macworld/posts/pfbid02j8qZVhnCk7xD2Gwq8nA9JDjDrNdcjNXa6bvUCDR1LsKRtrbbvFU2bdGHrffTRSd3l%20&amp;xcust=1-1-2158138-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></div>\n\n\n<div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aron-faine-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"aron faine facebook\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aron-faine-facebook.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 2400w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aron-faine-facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C104&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aron-faine-facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C266&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aron-faine-facebook.jpg?resize=1200%2C416&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aron-faine-facebook.jpg?resize=1536%2C532&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aron-faine-facebook.jpg?resize=2048%2C709&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"416\" /></figure><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.facebook.com/Macwo